Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:11.17,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wondering if you are lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:17.48,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}While waiting for my return
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:24.11,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Come,be one with me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:29.92,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Let us follow the path of light
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:36.29,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Mystery seeks to be understood
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:42.23,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Some day we'll find truth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:47.87,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wondering just who I might be
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:54.81,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Who I was and will become and
