Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:07.12,IN_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Move into the world above
Comment: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================↓IN(中)↓=================
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:58.65,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我怀疑我们是否是挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:05.57,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那点距离不能破坏我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:11.17,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我怀疑你是否孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:17.48,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}当你等待着我归来之时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:24.11,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}来，与我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:29.92,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}让我们跟随光的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:36.29,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被发现秘密追随
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:42.23,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}来日我们将找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:47.87,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我怀疑我是何物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:54.81,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我是谁 将来会变成怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:10:00.37,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我怀疑是否能继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:07.12,IN_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}步入天堂
Comment: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================↓ED(日)↓=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:55.28,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}なぜ 忘れたいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:23:01.16,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}ねえ 思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:14.03,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}あたたかい頬に降る 涙の願い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:19.53,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}なぜ ふるえながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:25.09,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}今 求めあうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:31.72,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}君だけを何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:37.21,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}抱きしめたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.53,0:23:43.65,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}蒼い星の海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:49.47,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}波間に漂う羽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:55.53,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}消えてゆく哀しみは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:24:00.91,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}明日への祈りなの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:06.16,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}Blueflow
Comment: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================↓ED(中)↓=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:55.28,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}为何想要忘却？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:23:01.16,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}请回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:14.03,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}那温暖的脸颊上滑落而下的泪之请愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:19.53,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}为何你在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:25.09,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}现在寻求着何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:31.72,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}只有你无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:37.21,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}都想与你相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.53,0:23:43.65,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}蔚蓝的星海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:49.47,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}波浪间漂浮的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:55.53,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}渐渐逝去的悲痛是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:24:00.91,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}向着明日的祈祷


